    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel? This car is a fantastic opportunity for anyone handy with a wrench! While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it\u2019s a solid foundation with plenty of potential for the right owner to bring back to life. Grab this bargain and make it your own today!",
