    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. It looks and feels brand new\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! If you're looking for perfection, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love with how it drives!",
