    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a factory limited-slip differential with zero lash. Structurally, the chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure maximum torsional rigidity. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, retains factory-spec compliance, offering the precise kinematics and tactile feedback expected of a showroom-quality M-division product. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
